{"tid":2505514,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BTS 突襲歌曲 Butter 5/21 發行","createTime":"2021-04-26T15:52:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T15:52:08.000Z","uid":1086,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e4c4992c26a6d3937a6db9f8ed17b506ae2bbe1b","tid":2505514,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T15:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/25HDnpI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F25HDnpI.jpg&h=9348b41e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NLcim9EPx6c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNLcim9EPx6c&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6wESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=ced6faa5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NLcim9EPx6c</a><br />\n<br />\n大家好，這裡是BIGHIT MUSIC。<br />\n<br />\n防彈少年團的數位單曲《Butter》將於2021年5月21日通過國內外音源網站正式發行。<br />\n<br />\n新單曲《Butter》是一首充滿著奶油般絲滑融入ARMY日常的防彈少年團魅力的歌曲。一同<br />\n享受並陷入時而溫柔，時而霸氣的防彈少年團的魅力之中吧！<br />\n<br />\n即將到來的夏日，《Butter》的實體唱片也將在國內外依次發售，請多多期待。<br />\n(發售時間根據各地區及各銷售點可能有所不同)<br />\n<br />\n感謝ARMY們對防彈少年團一如既往的喜愛，<br />\n<br />\nBTS的數位單曲《Butter》，望各位粉絲朋友們多多關注支持。<br />\n<br />\n發行時間: 2021年05月21日(週五) 下午1點(KST)<br />\n<br />\n謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreanPop/M.1619449284.A.F74.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ptt.cc%2Fbbs%2FKoreanPop%2FM.1619449284.A.F74.html&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6wESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=1d5105ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ptt.cc/bbs/KoreanPop/M.1619449284.A.F74.html</a>"}]}